@startuml sequence-license-issuance
title First-Time License Issuance - Sequence Diagram

actor "Licensing Employee" as Employee
boundary "DVLD UI" as UI
control "License Service" as LicenseService
control "Validation Service" as Validation
control "Test Service" as TestService
database "SQL Server Database" as DB

Employee -> UI : Create new license application
UI -> LicenseService : Submit application data
LicenseService -> Validation : Validate applicant eligibility
Validation -> DB : Check age, license class, duplicate applications
DB --> Validation : Validation result
Validation --> LicenseService : Eligibility result

alt Eligible applicant
  LicenseService -> TestService : Check required tests
  TestService -> DB : Verify vision, written, practical tests
  DB --> TestService : All tests passed
  TestService --> LicenseService : Tests passed
  LicenseService -> DB : Create driving license
  DB --> LicenseService : License created
  LicenseService --> UI : Display issued license
else Not eligible
  LicenseService --> UI : Display validation error
end

@enduml